metadata.name: ボディーペイント#一
metadata.description:
BodyPaint art fantasy! Discover the world of fantastic body art! 
Body art or body art is an artistic concept created as an artistic 
direction from the ideas of happening and flux. 
The body is as an art medium and art object, performance art, photography and video
 art where the artist inflicts injuries and pain on himself and works with his body as material.
